  "details": "<p>Image Field Caption (<code class=\"language-php\">image_field_caption</code>) adds an extra text area for captions on image fields.</p>\n<p>The module doesn't sanitize user input in certain cases, which leads to a Cross-Site-Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.</p>\n<p>The vulnerability is mitigated by several permissions, of which at least some are commonly only assigned to either editors, site builders or administrators.</p>",
